policy_contract.policy_insurance_text:
Canadian Premier Life Insurance Company, operating under the brand name Securian Canada (“Securian Canada”, “we”, “us” or “our”) has issued {product_name} Policy #{policy_num} (“Policy”) to {full_name} (“Policyholder”, “you”, “your”).

{product_prefix, select, ci{This Policy replaces and cancels any policy previously issued to you under Policy #{policy_num}.} other{This Policy supersedes any policy previously provided to you under Policy #{policy_num}.}}

If you are not satisfied with this Policy, you may cancel it by submitting a Cancellation Request Form to {administrator_name} (the Administrator) at any time.

{is_pm_partners_affiliate, select, True {} other {If you submit a Cancellation Request Form within 30 days of the Effective Date, you will receive a full refund of any premiums you have paid.}}
